    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We should be able to solve this by providing:\n- A way to update the configuration of a widget:\n\nSomething like widget.setConfiguration({conf})\n- A way to force a render of the interface.\n\nIf the configuration is different there will be a new request. TransformData on the hits widget runs again and you are able to switch the #price attribute you are using based on what the user selected in a custom widget.\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
