    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I would name it `updateConfiguration` (as to be clear that this is not the way to init a widget). What would be perfect would be to be able to update every configuration option, but I'm not sure how possible it will be (like changing the bound DOM container, the templates, etc).\n",
