    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "To solve this, I propose to have:\n- search.removeWidget(widget) that will remove the widget and clean any needed DOM/events\n\nThen you would just add a new slider with a different configuration.\n\nThis is a lot simpler and could be done for every widget.\n\nMoved to #1065\n",
